</li><li><a href="/wiki/index.php/Video_Fiction" title="Video Fiction">Video Fiction</a> - only indirectly linked to terrorism and counterterrorism
</li><li><a href="/wiki/index.php/Video_Documentaries" title="Video Documentaries">Video Documentaries</a>
</li><li><a href="/wiki/index.php/Short_videos" title="Short videos">Short videos</a> - TED and other</p>
</li></ul>

