<h1> <span class="mw-headline" id="Edited_and_Expanded_Transcripts">Edited and Expanded Transcripts</span></h1>
<p>I took the transcripts from the Reading Section, and did some edits. Removed repetitions (“ at the phenomenon, the new phenomenon” to “at the new phenomenon”), joined the dis-jointed sentences (“for vigorous debates. Critical self-reflexivity and alternative” to “for vigorous debates, critical self-reflexivity and alternative”), corrected a few mistakes (“who was hijacked. Who was taken hostage by” to “who was taken hostage by”, “real dominated” to “male dominated”), replaced [foreign] with the actual foreign terms, added some pictures / screenshots, added video quiz questions. This is far from perfect.</p>
<p>Please download the PDFs from <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://wp.me/pmMJ0-nB">http://wp.me/pmMJ0-nB</a></p>
<p>(Earlier, i gave the individual links. But when i update the files, the URL changes. It's cumbersome to keep changing URLs and also to keep adding this page)</p>
