<h1> <span class="mw-headline" id="Internet_and_terrorism">Internet and terrorism</span></h1>
<p>A research project produced as a thesis for a MSc in Information Security. I also created a thread in which we can discuss on this topic (<a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="https://class.coursera.org/terrorism-002/forum/thread?thread_id=430">https://class.coursera.org/terrorism-002/forum/thread?thread_id=430</a>)</p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.scribd.com/doc/196649598/Terrorist-use-of-the-Internet-an-analysis-of-the-current-threat-and-its-potential-evolution">Terrorist use of the Internet: an analysis of the current threatand its potential evolution</a></p>
<p>Research / Tags: Propaganda; Fundraising; Radicalisation; Secret communications; cyberterrorism</p>
<p></p>

